'''Jonathan Oliver''' is a British actor who appeared in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars: Episode IV'' ''Return of the Jedi'']]. He was credited as "Stardestroyer controller #2," though his character in reality served under [[Glyn Baker]]'s [[Endicott]] on the [[DS-2 Death Star II Mobile Battle Station|Second Death Star]].

